channel.title: y3ll0weye
channel.description: ctf player for Queen's University's Qu4cks team. Here you can find my writeups, projects and whatever else comes to mind.

item.title: UMDCTF 2025
item.description: Writeup for the crypto challenge obsidian-block and the pwn challenge aura from UMDCTF 2025 hosted by University of Maryland, College Park.

item.title: Dawg CTF 2025
item.description: Writeup for the crypto challenge The MAC FAC from DawgCTF 2025, hosted by University of Maryland. (Exams done so more writeups coming soon hopefully!)

item.title: PwnMe CTF 2025
item.description: Writeups for the pwn challenge GOT and the crypto challenges Easy Diffy and Square Power from the PwnMe 2025 capture the flag event.

item.title: Nullcon HackIM CTF Goa 2025
item.description: Writeups for the web challenge Numberizer and the crypto challenge kleinvieh from the Nullcon Goa 2025 capture the flag event.

item.title: Web Application analysis
item.description: In this project we create a data set of different technologies used in 1000 different websites with the goal of identifiying these technologies using machine learning. Follow along as we redefine our problems and reach an unsatisfying but important conclusion.

item.title: TryHackMe Cyborg
item.description: A box involving encrypted archives, source code analysis and more. Gain user and root access on this machine.

item.title: Sentiment analysis part 1
item.description: In this project we create, clean and analyze data in reddit comments from scratch, focusing on posts in the r/datascience subreddit. We aim to give quantitative meaning to our text data and analyze the results to see how people in r/datascience feel about jobs and the workplace.

item.title: Kioptrix
item.description: Gain root access on this vulnerable machine. Enumerate to find the vulnerablilities and then exploit them to pwn the machine.

item.title: Bandit lvl 18-20
item.description: Completing each level grants you the password for the next. Use Linux navigation skills to progress through the levels and solve the many challenges along the way.
